text: Hana Krejčová (born 15 March 1961) is a Czech rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
